To add breadcrumbs without a plugin

✅ Parent → Child Pages
✅ Posts with Categories
✅ Custom Post Types (CPT)
✅ Custom Taxonomies
✅ Taxonomy Terms hierarchy

This solution dynamically builds the full hierarchy across WordPress content types.


Step 1 — Add Advanced Breadcrumb Function

Go to:

Appearance → Theme File Editor → functions.php

Step 2 — Display Breadcrumbs in Theme

Now open:

header.php

Add This code:

<?php advanced_custom_breadcrumbs(); ?>
